\id 2PE - Mangga Buang NT [mmo] -Papua New Guinea 1981 (web 2014)
\h 2 Pita
\toc1 Pita-te kaapiya tu yuuh
\toc2 2 Pita
\toc3 2Pi
\mt1 Pita-te kaapiya tu yuuh
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Sa Simeon Pita, Yesu Kalisi-te omaaho kul ti osin yite sinaale sa. Sa kaavu kaapiyaa-jo laas vu ham sen ham awii-having-ambe Anutu hako ham lak, yik va timu nambe sen hako hey lak-ato. In yate Anutu sen hako yiiy lom-ato ond Yesu Kalisi, ond yi omaaho nivalok vulﺣﺑﺣﺑt ondeey wiing-ambe ham awii-having.
\p 
\v 2 + o 1:2 Jut 2*Ham oo anjak Anutu yuuh yate Omaaho Bop Yesuu-to nind lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, de yuuh lambiing samu samu naas mando gaving ham-ambe ham alompayo nanjip melaas keen, be mem naatu bopaata jak.
\s1 Anutu yoo holin yiiy lak in nambe yaambiing va nohvu ka
\p 
\v 3 + o 1:3 1Pi 2:9*Lak Anutu-te niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k sen Kalisi wiing-ambe yaalohvu in nambe yiiy mando monaambiing va sapa Anutu kaa-to, ondeey Anutu wiing-ambe yalak omaaho sen teey yiiy-ato ni, ond teey yiiy in nambe yiiy naatu hil anikaapulis osin hil anivasa nﺣﺑﺣﺑn naambe yii-to.
\v 4 Om nambﺣ۹ﺣ۹njo ond Anutu yoo jﺣﺑﺣﺑy yite vakasin bo-bop osin vakasin anivasa vasa vu yiiy naambe yale naatovu nﺣﺑﺣﺑn, le mem ham e anoh nanye in va nipaya lﺣﺑﺣﺑt sen laam vu omaahonﺣﺑﺣﺑn alondpayo navu navu be neep ngeeyaata vu voon-anjﺣﺑﺣﺑto, tonde ham naatu hil anivasa osin hil anivalok naambe Anutu.
\p 
\v 5 Om sen ham awii-having Kalisii-to, ond ham animwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k lﺣﺑﺣﺑt-ambe ham gako kakook anivasa, tombe mem ham oo monambiing va nivasa mu,
\v 6 + o 1:6 Gal 5:22-23*om ham oo anjakin ham nivasa, tonde ham baale niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k-ambe ham baaku nimeen pin, be mem ham oo monambiing va pin sapa Anutu ka,
\v 7 tonde ham ahem gaving halim-aso bel-ate osin ham ahem gaving hil pin.
\p 
\v 8 Ke, naambe ham atu hil nambﺣ۹ﺣ۹njo be ham oo navu samu va pin-anjo nivasa lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, ond va sen ham alak yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi nii-to me-tu va malis e, nganjo nayiis nﺣﺑﺣﺑn anivasa vasa.
\v 9 Lemu omaaho ti sen nativak in kul anivasaa-jo de me-nawiing e, ond me-nayi taaku nivasa le, mekanu, tonde yite va nipaya sen yoo nawiing bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ato ond Anutu kawiiy la lung la, le ma de ka lingin nambe mak Anutu me-kawiiy la le.
\p 
\v 10 Om halingg-aso, ham ambiing kul aniwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k in nambe va sen Anutu holin ham-ambe teey ham in-ato, ond yoo nanjip niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k. Ke, ham ambiing naambﺣ۹ﺣ۹njo ond mem ham-ame le ana mem nama le,
\v 11 nganjo Anutu le tatekin mopaatﺣﺑﺣﺑv vu ham in nambe gako ham jak-ambe ham andukana yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi sen hako yiiy lom-ato yite taaku, be mem yoo ganggin ham danggata osin danggata.
\p 
\v 12 + o 1:12 Jut 5*Om sa kangg vu nambe soo le aambﺣ۹ﺣ۹l ham alum jak in vakasin-anjo jak busin pin. Keen, ham alak vakasin-anjo ni lung la, be ham naale niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k in vakasin keen sen ham hako lung laa-to,
\v 13 + o 1:13 2Pi 3:1*lemu sa kangg vu nambe busin sen sa mando voon-anjo, ond soo monaambﺣ۹ﺣ۹l ham alum jak in vakasin-anjo ond mem nivasa.
\v 14 + o 1:14 2Ko 5:1; Jon 21:18-19*In sa lak ni nambe busin sen sa gavuuh voon-anjo be sanaa-to ond ngaaho lak, yik lohvu sen yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi yoo taato langaah vu sa lung laa-to.
\v 15 Om soo le monaambﺣ۹ﺣ۹l ham alum jak lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, be sa gavuuh ham na vﺣ۹ﺣ۹l e mem sate vakasin yoo nanjip in nambe ham akam monambu.
\s1 Pita-so layi Kalisi-te nikaapulis
\p 
\v 16 + o 1:16-18 Mat 17:1-5*Hey aanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vu ham nambe yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi ond yi omaaho niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k, tombe le dukanom, ond hey-ame aanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l sapa vakasin hatulin malis heey sen hil osin kand oo lanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l-ato le, nganjo hey aahe mengg ak yite nikaapulis bopaata lung la.
\v 17 In busin sen Mangganaan Anutu hako yi lak-ambe vu nikaapulis vu yii-to,
\p ond Anutuu-ju Omaaho Nikaapulis danggakook lava laam vu yi nambe, ﻗSa noongg-anja, sahengg having yi lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, osin sahengg anivasa vu yi.ﻗ
\v 18 Ond lavaa-ju laam vu baandoni be hey hangoyin, in hey ala nando lak kandu vaambuung-anju lu having yi,
\v 19 ondeey hey alak ni nambe Anutu-te vakasin sen hil lanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l langaah bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ato ond nﺣﺑﺣﺑn keen. In silate vakasin ond lohvu kin natum hﺣﺑﺣﺑk taaku mekanu, om ham oo gambe nanyem in silate vakasin anivasa lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, be na balup busin sen taaku ahelangaah jak-ande matam samiinaanﺣﺑﺣﺑn-ate naatum dukana ham alompayﺣﺑﺣﺑ-to.
\p 
\v 20 Lemu ham gango le, Anutu-te vakasin pin sen hil lanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l langaah-ambe neep hﺣﺑﺣﺑk kaapiyaa-to ond omaaho ti me-yoo lohvu nambe tatekin danggakook e,
\v 21 + o 1:21 2Ti 3:16; 1Pi 1:11*in silate vakasin ond omaaho ti me-yoo lopayo haanjiihin yi be nﺣ۹ﺣ۹l e, malis lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, yik Vavi Vaambuung oo vﺣ۹ﺣ۹l sil alund ak e mem lanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vakasin sen Anutu vu vu sil-ato.
\c 2
\s1 Hil tanasin tatuhin vaha-sote mopaatﺣﺑﺣﺑv anipaya
\p 
\v 1 + o 2:1 Mat 24:11; Jut 4*Bﺣﺑﺣﺑy ond hil tanasin tatuhin vaha-so vaalu kandi hﺣﺑﺣﺑk hil lavuun, tombe yik ham ond hil tanasin tatuhin vaha-so vaalu le kandi in nambe taahu ham hﺣﺑﺣﺑk silate vakasin tatuhin. Sil e daanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l tanasib anipaya sen le biing pasiivu hil-ato, osin daatu kand in Omaaho Bop sen vaanggo sil lom-ato, om silate nipayaa-ju yoo le gako sil-ambe lana mend nama valok-ate pavis.
\v 2 Lemu hil ngeeyaata le sapa sil vahand-ambe yoo lambiing baayamb danje-danjeen, tombe lak silate va nipayaa-ju sen hil e daanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l Anutu-te mop keen-ato pale.
\v 3 + o 2:3 Lom 16:18; 1Tes 2:5*Tatuhin vaha mend nﺣﺑﺣﺑn-asﺣﺑﺣﺑnju le daanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vakasin tatuhin vu ham-ambe gako mone jak. Omaaho sen gangoyin silate vakasin-ambe naanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l naambe sil gako nipaya nyevahaan-ato, ond vu bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ambe tok laam gﺣ۹ﺣ۹n-anjo, ond me-neep paling e, nganjo yoo samu yi lung la, yik omaaho sen le nyiis sil-ambe lana mend nama valok-atﺣ۹ﺣ۹to ond me-neep me le.
\p 
\v 4 + o 2:4 Jut 6*Bﺣﺑﺣﺑy sen angela-so vaalu lawiing va nipayaa-to ond Anutu me-ka pasiv in sil e, nganjo luus sil-ambe lalukala taaku nipaya. Yik duuh sil-ambe dando hﺣﺑﺣﺑk mekanuu-ju be mondanggin busin sen Anutu bu nyevahaan dukanaah hil pin-ate vakasin-ato.
\v 5 + o 2:5 Jen 6:11ﻗ8:19; 2Pi 3:6*Tonde yik hil sen dando hﺣﺑﺣﺑk Noa-te busin bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ato ond laluuh damind vu Anutu, ond Anutu me-ka pasiv in sil e, nganjo wiing-ambe bel vuuk-ambe yiis sil pin-ambe layimb, de hanggin Noa sen tatekin mop anivalok-ate langaah vu hil-o having yite hil namaavaalu be vindak yuuh amuu-to be sil dando nivasa.
\v 6 + o 2:6 Jen 19:24; Jut 7*Tonde hil Sodom ayuuh Gomolaa-to, ond Anutu nﺣ۹ﺣ۹l nambe daatovu silate nipaya nyevahaan-ambe lana mend nama, ondeey wiing-ambe kin ya taaku yuuh-anju be lung la valok-ate, tombe manyinju tu taahu taahu in nambe hil sen galuuh damind vu Anutu vu taamusin-ato lanji be lanjﺣ۹ﺣ۹nin naambe me-sapa hﺣﺑﺣﺑk sil vahand e.
\v 7 + o 2:7 Jen 19:1-16*Tonde omaaho nivalok Lot ond lopayo nimeen lﺣﺑﺣﺑt in hil Sodom ayuuh Gomola-te va nipaya sen dawiing-ambe davu sapa mop baayamb-ato, ond Anutu vu vﺣ۹ﺣ۹l yi in kin sen ya sil-ato be nando nivasa.
\v 8 In omaaho nivalok Lot-anju ond nando having sil, om yoo monango be nayi va nipaya sen dawiing-anju, tombe nawiing-ambe lopayo nimeen lﺣﺑﺣﺑt nalak busin pin.
\v 9 + o 2:9 1Ko 10:13; Jut 6*Ke, om Omaaho Bop oo lak ni nambe hil sen davu sapa kaa-to ond nalﺣﺑﺣﺑh sil vﺣ۹ﺣ۹l in nimeen sen navu sahi sil-ato, tonde hil sen me-davu sapa mop anivalok-ato ond yoo navu nipaya nyevahaan vu sil lﺣﺑﺣﺑt-ambe na balup busin sen Anutu gangoyin hil pin-ate vakasin-ato.
\v 10 + o 2:10 Jut 7-8,16*Ond yik yoo le bu nivaane bopaata lﺣﺑﺣﺑt vu hil sen davu sapa hﺣﺑﺣﺑk va nipaya sen nind naavi nipaya voon-ate navu navu in-ambe sil dayi Omaaho Bop nambe va malis-ato.
\p Tatuhin ambu-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju ond yoo datee sil ak lﺣﺑﺣﺑt-ambe dawiing va lohvu sil akand, me-dayﺣ۹ﺣ۹nin angela baandoni-so daka le, nganjo danﺣ۹ﺣ۹l sil pale.
\v 11 + o 2:11 Jut 9*Tonde sim angela-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju sil haalend bop osin silate niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k ond bopaata savok, lemu sil-ame danﺣ۹ﺣ۹l tatuhin vaha-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju pale hﺣﺑﺣﺑk Anutu me be davu talﺣﺑﺣﺑt sil nambe lana mend nama lﺣﺑﺣﺑt e.
\v 12 + o 2:12 Jut 10*Tatuhin ambu-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju yoo mondawiing va sen londpayo naanjiihin sil in-ato, om sil lalohvu
\p vahivak sen lundkook maa-to, om taandin lako sil e sim lahﺣﺑﺣﺑk jaang-ambe hil layiis sil. Hil-anju ond danﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vakasin anipaya danjeen lak va pin sen sil doosin danggakook-ato, tombe silate va nipaya le naatu ganggweeng-ambe nyiis sil, tombe lanjimb valok-ate.
\v 13 + o 2:13 Jut 12*Sil e gako nipaya dukanaah silate va nipaya nyevahaan. Sil oo kand vasa be dawiing va sen londpayo navu navu in-ato hﺣﺑﺣﺑk taaku langaah. Sil anipaya be yoo dawiing va sen nimumin-atﺣ۹ﺣ۹to, tonde dalukalaas-ambe daya vanﺣﺑﺣﺑn having ham, tombe dapﺣ۹ﺣ۹lis in silate mop tatuhin-ate.
\v 14 Sil amend kaalus oo nala vu vﺣ۹ﺣ۹h baayamb-aso, de mend oo navu salo va nipaya in nambe lambiing lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, tonde danjinj hil vaalu sen me-dawii-having Anutu niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k-ato be davu sapa sil vahand, tombe sil amend nﺣﺑﺣﺑn-anju tu niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k hﺣﺑﺣﺑk sil alondpayo. Ke, Anutu talﺣﺑﺣﺑt hil-anju lung la om sil e gako nipaya valok-ate.
\v 15 + o 2:15 Nam 22:7; Jut 11; Taato 2:14*Sil lavuuh mop anivalok la de davu sapa Bosol noow Belam-ate mopaatﺣﺑﺣﺑv, sen yoo ahe having nambe gako mone jak yite va nipayaa-to,
\v 16 + o 2:16 Nam 22:28-35*om Anutu nﺣ۹ﺣ۹l omaahﺣﺑﺣﺑ-ju in yite va nipaya. In bik donggi ti me-lohvu nambe bakaas e, le ma de vakaas omaahonﺣﺑﺣﺑn lava be hilin va sen omaahﺣﺑﺣﺑ-ju lukook ma be wiingin nambe biing-ato.
\p 
\v 17 + o 2:17 Jut 12-13*Hil tatuhin vaha-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju ond sil lalohvu bel hatuusin osin bayiimb sen vavi jamba navﺣ۹ﺣ۹-to, om Anutu samu taaku mekanu nipaya valok-ate be nando nanggin sil.
\v 18 + o 2:18 Jut 16*Sil oo dakaas avind bop-ambe danﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vakasin hateesin sen nﺣﺑﺣﺑn maa-to, tonde danjinj hil vaalu sen daahen dapak gesaange in hil ango-te mopaatﺣﺑﺣﺑv anipayaa-to. Ond danjinj sil ak silate mop sen davu sapa hﺣﺑﺣﺑk naavind nipaya navu navu voon-ate be dawiing baayamb danje-danjeen-ato, in nambe sil taamuyin tatuhin vaha-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju vahand.
\v 19 + o 2:19 Jon 8:34*Hil tatuhin vaha-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju danﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vu hil nambe
\p sil e kavaayin hees in sil-ambe vati me-le naanduuh sil naah e. Lemu tatuhin vaha-sﺣﺑﺣﺑnju yoo latu va nipaya sen le gako sil-ambe lana mend namaa-to yite hil kul malis amu lung la, in va nipaya laanggﺣﺑﺣﺑl omaaho ti, ond omaahﺣﺑﺣﺑ-ju tu va nipaya-te hil kul malis amu lung la.
\v 20 + o 2:20 Mat 12:45*Naambe hil lalak yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi sen hako yiiy lom-ato ni, be sil lavuuh va nipaya voon-ate la lung la, le sim sil lalukalaah va nipayaa-ju be laanggﺣﺑﺣﺑl sil yesin laah, ond bﺣﺑﺣﺑy sil doosin Kalisi ond sil dando paya, tombe sim sil lalak Kalisi ni le ma de laluuh damind vu, ond mem sil dando nipaya valok-ate lﺣﺑﺣﺑt.
\v 21 + o 2:21 Luk 12:47-48*Le naambe hil-anju doosin mopaatﺣﺑﺣﺑv anivalok, ond sil-ame le daatovu nipaya nyevahaan lﺣﺑﺣﺑt e, lemu hil-anju lalak mopaatﺣﺑﺣﺑv anivalok ani lung la, le ma de laluuh damind vu Anutu-te vakasin vaambuung sen vu vu sil-ato, om sil e daatovu nipaya nyevahaan valok-ate.
\v 22 + o 2:22 Pro 26:11*Om va sen tovu sil-ato ond lohvu himbop-ate navu dangga keen ti neep nambe, ﻗVoow oo daya silate va sen damutak laa-to yesin laah.ﻗ De ango nambe, ﻗBik sen luus bel lung laa-to ond laah nali malﺣﺑﺣﺑmak yesin laah.ﻗ
\c 3
\s1 Omaaho Bop e dukanom keen lﺣﺑﺣﺑt
\p 
\v 1 + o 3:1 2Pi 1:13*Sate va-so, sa kaavu kaapiya ti vu ham bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ato, le mem gﺣ۹ﺣ۹n sa kaavu angﺣﺑﺣﺑ-jo vu ham yesin laah, ond kakook anivasa neep vu ham, lemu sa kaavu in nambe saambﺣ۹ﺣ۹l ham alum jak
\v 2 + o 3:2 Jut 17*in ham akam bu vakasin sen hil vaambuung-aso lanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l langaah bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ato, osin Omaaho Bop sen hako yiiy lom-ato yite vakasin sen hamate sinaale-so lanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l vu ham-ato.
\v 3 + o 3:3 1Ti 4:1; Jut 18*Om ham gango le, busin taamusin ond palesin ambu-so le lanaam-ambe mosapa va sen londpayo naanjiihin sil in-ato, be daanﺣ۹ﺣ۹l ham pale
\v 4 + o 3:4 Ais 5:19; Esi 12:22; Mat 24:48*naambe, ﻗKalisi nﺣ۹ﺣ۹l nambe le nom gato, le me-lo-hato le? De yate himbop-aso bﺣﺑﺣﺑy layimb lung la, lemu va pin sen Anutu hatung bﺣﺑﺣﺑy-ato ond yoo naahen neep timu be tok valup gﺣ۹ﺣ۹n-anjo.ﻗ
\v 5 + o 3:5 Jen 1:6-9*Ke, silate vakasin-anju, lemu sil oo daluuh damind vu va sen Anutu yoo nﺣ۹ﺣ۹l lava bﺣﺑﺣﺑy lﺣﺑﺣﺑt-ambe yendak nandﺣﺑﺣﺑ-to, tonde ngaanggis kandi lak hﺣﺑﺣﺑk bel lavuun-ambe nando,
\v 6 + o 3:6 Jen 7:11-21; 2Pi 2:5*le sim taamusin bel vuuk-ambe savun ngaanggis munggin-anju pin-ambe la mema valok-ate.
\v 7 Nganjo ngaanggis osin yendak sen nando gﺣ۹ﺣ۹n-anjo, ond yik Anutu nﺣ۹ﺣ۹l-ambe yoo nando nivasa be nanggin busin sen kin e jaa-to, in Anutu le sahi hil pin-ate vakasin-ambe juus omaahonﺣﺑﺣﺑn sen laluuh damind vu yii-to, be mem lana mend nama valok-ate.
\p 
\v 8 + o 3:8 Saam 90:4*Lemu sate va-so, ham akam-ame jingin vakasin tii-jo le nambe, Omaaho Bop nayi nambe busin nﺣﺑﺣﺑn timu ond lohvu ta ngeeyaata lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, tonde ta ngeeyaata ond yik yuuh busin nﺣﺑﺣﺑn timu laloh ti.
\v 9 + o 3:9 Hab 2:3; 1Ti 2:4*De Omaaho Bop-ame wiing yite vakasin sen jﺣﺑﺣﺑy bﺣﺑﺣﺑy nambe le nom gatﺣﺑﺣﺑ-to nﺣﺑﺣﺑn ak e, ond me-yoo nawiing nime-meen nambe sen hil vaalu kand navu nambe naahen nawiing nimeen-ato le, nganjo yoo monapuvu yi tatin-ambe nanggin ham lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, in nimbaya nambe omaaho ti me-na menama le, nganjo yoo wiingin nambe hil pin langgilin londpayo naah vu yi
\p vﺣ۹ﺣ۹l e.
\s1 Ngaanggis osin yendak-anjo le nama na
\p 
\v 10 + o 3:10 1Tes 5:2; Mat 24:29,35*Omaaho Bop-ate busin e naatok naam nohvu omaaho hﺣﺑﺣﺑndak ti, tombe yendak e biing puung-ambe na menama, tonde kin e ja va pin sen nando hﺣﺑﺣﺑk yendak-ato be jung na. De ngaanggis osin omaahonﺣﺑﺣﺑn-ate kul ayuuh ame pin, ond yik kin e ja be jung na lﺣﺑﺣﺑt.
\p 
\v 11 Ke, Anutu le kawiiy va pin-anju na, om ham oo taamuyin mop vaambuung-ate be ham mando monambiing va sapa Anutu ka.
\v 12 + o 3:12 Ais 34:4*Om ham oo monggatung mem in Anutu-te busin-ambe ham ambiing kul aniwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k in nambe naatok naam pavis, tombe busin-anju ond kin e ja yendak-ambe jung na, de va pin sen nando hﺣﺑﺣﺑk-ato ond kin e ja be jung na valok-ate.
\v 13 + o 3:13 Ais 65:17; 66:22; Taato 21:1,27*Lemu yiiy oo monatung mengg in yendak moos osin ngaanggis moos sen hil anivalok amu yoo baand-ato in nambe naatok naam, in Anutu yoo jﺣﺑﺣﺑy vakasin ak lung la.
\s1 Yiiy samu yiiy-ambe yiiy gatung mengg in Omaaho Bop
\p 
\v 14 Sate va-so, ham nanggin Anutu-te busin-anju om ham samu ham nivasa lﺣﺑﺣﺑt, in nambe Anutu ji naambe ham alompayo nikaapiikaanﺣﺑﺣﺑn-ande va nipaya ti me-neep vu ham e, nganjo le ji naambe ham alompayo neep melaas.
\v 15 + o 3:15 Lom 2:4; 2Pi 3:9*Tombe va sen Omaaho Bop napuvu yi tatin-ambe nanggin lﺣﺑﺣﺑt-ato, ond ham anjak ni naambe nanggin in nambe hil pin langgilin sil vasa be gako sil naah, yik lohvu vakasin sen Anuu vu kakook vu yiiy halingg anivasa Pol, tombe sapa hﺣﺑﺣﺑk-ambe kaavu laas vu ham-ato.
\v 16 Ond kaavu vakasin lak vaa-jo be neep hﺣﺑﺣﺑk yite kaapiya pin.
\p Tombe vakasin vaalu sen neep hﺣﺑﺣﺑk Pol-ate kaapiyaa-to ond danggakook vun yi, tombe hil sen kand ma be londpayo yuyuuh-ato ond davu tatekin Pol-ate vakasin animeen-anju paya, yik nambe sen davu tatekin Anutu-te vakasin vaalu pin payaa-to, om silate vakasin tatuhin-anju le gako sil-ambe lana mend nama.
\p 
\v 17 + o 3:17 Mak 13:5,33; 1Ko 10:12*Sate va-so, ham alak vakasin-anjo ni lung la, om ham ganggin ham in nambe ham-ame sapa hﺣﺑﺣﺑk kalﺣ۹ﺣ۹sin ambu-sote vakasin tatuhin e, in le gako ham na paya, de ham-ame le baale niwﺣ۹ﺣ۹k in va sen ham awii-having lung laa-to jesin naah e.
\v 18 + o 3:18 Jut 25*Om yik ham oo gako samu samu osin kakook anivasa vu yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi sen hako yiiy lom-ato, be mem ham oo ambiing-ambe nﺣﺑﺣﺑn jak lﺣﺑﺣﺑt. Yik Kalisii-ju yite nikaapulis naatu bopaata vu peey-anjo be nanjip danggata. Keen. 
